<p>PayPhoneAPP respects your privacy and works hard to protect your personal information. We want you to understand how we may collect, store, use and protect any personal information. We will not share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy. When you downloaded our software in order to use our services you agreed to accept this policy. We may change this policy at any time. We will post notifications of revised versions of our policy on our website, and revised policies will be immediately effective. Throughout this Privacy Policy, we will refer to our website, software, and services collectively as the Service. Please note, this Privacy Policy does not apply to information we collect by other means than your use of the Service (including offline) or from other sources.</p>

